@Venkatesh Closing out the loop here - The ICD-10 code app has been updated to indicate that it only processes German ICD codes.

Based on Travis' reply to this thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05BJCNKZAM/p1716922628680039?thread_ts=1716922318.606809&cid=C05BJCNKZAM), we currently don't support sample docs for advanced apps.
